reviewText: Product performed as described and met all my expectations. I would purchase again
This is a great DVD I love the robertsons and what they stand for. Jesus is Lord!
The disc had pour audio.  It was hard to hear the guys talking without maxing out the volume control.

I still wish they would start putting in more interviews and commentary more like Benelli Duck Commander or Duck Dynasty.  95% shooting, 5% talking.  But if you want to watch them hunt, this is a good one to buy.
I always enjoy the adventure of the season and watching them overcome the obstacles of hunting. It is relatable to every hunter that ever set foot in a swamp.
These videos are simple but the cool thing about it is the feeling of being there. Millions of people love the Duck boys and if you love hunting you will love these videos.
Funny and informative! The Robertsons et al, could make the drabbest subject enjoyable. We'll be ordering more from this family!
I ordered this for my husband for his birthday. He hunts every year and has all of the Duckmen Videos.  Out of all his videos Duckmen are the only ones that I will watch. LOL
